attachments.title: This 3D Printed Subaru Flat-Four Engine Is Deeply Satisfying
attachments.text: The magical, almost Star Trek-replicator quality of 3D printing is still new enough to be novel and exciting, and one of the best parts about seeing fascinating 3D-printed stuff, like this Subaru EJ20 WRX engine, is knowing that, if you have a 3D printer, you could download it and have one of your very own. We live in the future.
